drop index 客户贷款_PK on ClientLoans;


alter table ClientLoans
drop foreign key FK_CLIENTLO_客户贷款_LOANS;

alter table ClientLoans
drop foreign key FK_CLIENTLO_客户贷款2_CLIENT;

drop table if exists ClientLoans;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: ClientLoans */
/*==============================================================*/
create table ClientLoans
(
loan_id varchar(60) not null comment '',
client_id varchar(20) not null comment ''
);

/*==============================================================*/
/* Index: 客户贷款_PK */
/*==============================================================*/
create unique index 客户贷款_PK on ClientLoans
(
loan_id,
client_id
);

alter table ClientLoans add constraint FK_CLIENTLO_客户贷款_LOANS foreign key (loan_id)
references loans (loan_id) on delete restrict on update restrict;

alter table ClientLoans add constraint FK_CLIENTLO_客户贷款2_CLIENT foreign key (client_id)
references client (client_id) on delete restrict on update restrict;
